    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Download?</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      Get instant access to the complete guide and start your PE fundraising journey with confidence.
    </p>
    <a href={pdfUrl} download class="download-cta">
