          Your definitive private equity placement agents resource.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-section">
        <h3>Resources</h3>
        <ul class="footer-links">
          <li><a href="/articles">Articles & Insights</a></li>
          <li><a href="/private-equity-placement-agents">Agency Directory</a></li>
          <li><a href="/resources/placement-agents-guide">Free PDF Guide</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-section">
        <h3>Company</h3>
        <ul class="footer-links">
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-section">
